# api-endpoints

Key API Endpoints and Business Logic:

## Meeting Management (Importance: 85)
File: src/app/routes/meetings.py

- Structured signal extraction during meeting creation
- Auto-categorization of extracted content into:
  - Decisions
  - Action items 
  - Blockers
  - Key risks
  - Ideas
  - Context
- Meeting transcript processing with dual-source handling
- Screenshot analysis integration with meeting context

## Document Processing (Importance: 80)
File: src/app/routes/documents.py

- Custom signal extraction pipeline for documents
- Business-specific document categorization system
- Integration with knowledge graph for relationship mapping
- Document-to-signal extraction with meeting associations

## Ticket Lifecycle (Importance: 75)
File: src/app/routes/tickets.py

- Sprint-based task decomposition
- Custom timeboxing calculations
- Code file version tracking per ticket
- Working days calculation excluding weekends

## Signal Processing (Importance: 90)
File: src/app/routes/signals.py

- Domain-specific signal classification
- Signal evolution tracking through states:
  - Pending
  - Approved
  - Rejected
  - Archived
  - Completed
- Signal aggregation based on business dates
- Meeting-to-signal relationship management

